arcade.agent.helper

Class InsertHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.helper.InsertHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Helper, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class InsertHelper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Helper
    Implementation of Helper for inserting cell populations.

    InsertHelper is stepped once. The InsertHelper will insert a mixture of the cell from the specified populations into locations within the specified radius from the center of the simulation.

    Since:
    2.2
    Version:
    2.3.7
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
